EN: We need to fill out a survey.
ZH: 请您仔细阅读每一道问卷问题。
EN: Please read each survey question carefully.
ZH: 问卷内容涉及到个人隐私，请如实填写。
EN: The survey content involves personal privacy, please fill it out truthfully.
ZH: 这份问卷需要大约十分钟填写。
EN: This survey will take about ten minutes to complete.
ZH: 请在规定时间内完成问卷填写。
EN: Please complete the survey within the specified time.
ZH: 问卷调查结果将作为研究数据。
EN: The survey results will be used as research data.
ZH: 问卷调查的结果对我们的工作至关重要。
EN: The results of the survey are crucial to our work.
ZH: 我们将根据问卷结果做出相应的改进。
EN: We will make improvements based on the survey results.
ZH: 请在空白处填写您的答案。
EN: Please fill in your answers in the blank spaces.
ZH: 问卷调查结果将完全保密。
EN: The survey results will be kept completely confidential.
ZH: 请勿在问卷上涂改或篡改任何内容。
EN: Do not alter or tamper with any content on the survey.
ZH: 请审慎思考后再填写问卷。
EN: Please think carefully before filling out the survey.
